{"id":292970,"url":"http://bgm.tv/subject/292970","type":2,"name":"魔女の旅々","name_cn":"魔女之旅","summary":"あるところに一人の旅人がいました。彼女の名はイレイナ。\r\n若くして魔法使いの最上位「魔女」となった才女です。\r\n幼いころに読んだ旅の物語に憧れて、\r\n流されるように気ままな長い旅を続けています。\r\nこの広大な世界を自由に渡り歩き、わけのわからない可笑しな人や、\r\n誰かの美しい日常に触れながら、\r\n彼女は旅人として、これといった目的もなく、\r\n色々な国や人との出逢いを繰り返します。\r\nそして同じ数だけの——\r\n\r\n「構わないでください。私、旅人なものですから。先を急がなければ\r\nならないのです」\r\nそんな魔女イレイナが紡ぐ、出逢いと別れの物語…。","air_date":"2020-10-02","air_weekday":5,"rating":{"total":605,"count":{"1":3,"2":2,"3":7,"4":21,"5":32,"6":102,"7":182,"8":200,"9":38,"10":18},"score":7.1},"rank":1956,"images":{"large":"http://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/l/99/17/292970_mxMxx.jpg","common":"http://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/99/17/292970_mxMxx.jpg","medium":"http://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/99/17/292970_mxMxx.jpg","small":"http://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/s/99/17/292970_mxMxx.jpg","grid":"http://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/g/99/17/292970_mxMxx.jpg"},"collection":{"wish":343,"collect":47,"doing":2102,"on_hold":41,"dropped":109},"crt":[{"id":72355,"url":"http://bgm.tv/character/72355","name":"イレイナ","name_cn":"伊蕾娜","role_name":"主角","images":{"large":"http://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/35/0e/72355_crt_6Z6zM.jpg?r=1602429332","medium":"http://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/m/35/0e/72355_crt_6Z6zM.jpg?r=1602429332","small":"http://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/s/35/0e/72355_crt_6Z6zM.jpg?r=1602429332","grid":"http://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/35/0e/72355_crt_6Z6zM.jpg?r=1602429332"},"comment":43,"collects":94,"info":{"name_cn":"伊蕾娜","alias":{"zh":"灰之魔女","en":"Elaina","jp":"灰の魔女"},"gender":"女","birth":"10月17日","source":"https://majotabi.jp/"},"actors":[{"id":19560,"url":"http://bgm.tv/person/19560","name":"本渡楓","images":{"large":"http://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/l/1a/96/19560_prsn_ZkOj3.jpg?r=1553731935","medium":"http://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/m/1a/96/19560_prsn_ZkOj3.jpg?r=1553731935","small":"http://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/s/1a/96/19560_prsn_ZkOj3.jpg?r=1553731935","grid":"http://lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/1a/96/19560_prsn_ZkOj3.jpg?r=1553731935"}}]},{"id":72356,"url":"http://bgm